result:
<v-container
  grid-list-xl
>
  <v-layout wrap>
    <v-flex xs12>
      <slot />
    </v-flex>

    <feed-card
      v-for="(article, i) in paginatedArticles"
      :key="article.title"
      :size="layout[i]"
      :value="article"
    />
  </v-layout>

  <v-layout align-center>
    <v-flex xs3>
      <base-btn
        v-if="page !== 1"
        class="ml-0"
        title="Previous page"
        square
        @click="page--"
      >
        <v-icon>mdi-chevron-left</v-icon>
      </base-btn>
    </v-flex>

    <v-flex
      xs6
      text-xs-center
      subheading
    >
      PAGE {{ page }} OF {{ pages }}
    </v-flex>

    <v-flex
      xs3
      text-xs-right
    >
      <base-btn
        v-if="pages > 1 && page < pages"
        class="mr-0"
        title="Next page"
        square
        @click="page++"
      >
        <v-icon>mdi-chevron-right</v-icon>
      </base-btn>
    </v-flex>
  </v-layout>
</v-container>
